title: [SOLVED]820-00165 no power
message:
how long is that "quickly"? 
Could be bad Q7560 (you should also check if both gates are ok, sorry, you need an oscilloscope for that),
check R7516, R7546, C7588
also, if you're checking voltages with an oscilloscope, you're seeing "wobbly" voltage almost everywere
